data.title: Great beer run by great people
data.text: Todd and his wife Gwen run a great place. Beautiful bar with a great selection of beers not available anywhere else in the QC. A great place to sit and talk with friends without the painful noise of TVs blaring above your heads. No food menu, but you can bring in your own.

data.title: Thumbs up!
data.text: Great selection of brews, both local and abroad.  20 bears on tap plus many off sale as well. Visited on my own during special event where they were showcasing sixpoint brewery.  Knowledgeable staff!
